# Red Hat Training Lab Grading Infrastructure

## Lab Grading Framework

### Purpose
This framework provides the lab grading infrastructure
for Red Hat Training courseware. The tools in this library
allow the student to grade the progress of their lab work
in their classroom lab environment.

### How to develop lab scripts?

Start learning your way around the framework with the [Lab Grading Framework Training](docs/training/README.adoc).

If you are already familiar with the framework, please read the [development guide](docs/development/README.adoc).

If you are releasing a new version, then read the [publish guide](docs/development/PUBLISH.adoc).

### Contributing

Read the [development guide](docs/development/README.adoc).


